{
  "info": {
    "name": "Api-Orquestrador — Audit Log",
    "_postman_id": "audit-log-2026-06-20",
    "description": "Testes da feature de audit log contra https://orcapi.martiellima.com/.\n\nSCHEMA COMPLETO (introspection desabilitada em prod): ver docs/api-schema-reference.md no repo.\nDOWNLOAD DO SCHEMA (SDL para autocomplete no Postman): schema.graphql na raiz do repo.\nGUIA DETALHADO DE SESSAO (login, refresh, troubleshooting): docs/session-management.md.\n\nNOTA: Apollo Server 4+ tem CSRF protection. A collection ja envia os 2 headers necessarios:\n- Content-Type: application/json (parse do body)\n- apollo-require-preflight: true (bypass CSRF)\n\nAUTENTICACAO: rode 'Login (admin)' primeiro. Ele salva {{token}} (accessToken, 15min) E {{refreshToken}} (refreshToken, 7d) nas variaveis da collection. Os requests autenticados ja enviam 'Authorization: Bearer {{token}}' no header.\n\nAUTO-REFRESH: a collection tem um Pre-request Script no nivel da collection que detecta {{token}} expirado (ou faltando) e chama 'mutation refresh' automaticamente antes de cada request. Nao precisa re-logar manualmente a cada 15min.\n\nSe uma request retornar 'UNAUTHENTICATED', confira:\n1. Voce rodou 'Login (admin)' nesta sessao? {{token}} deve estar preenchido em Edit Collection > Variables.\n2. Authorization no header e 'Bearer {{token}}' (sem prefixo Bearer duplicado).\n3. baseUrl esta apontando pro servidor certo (tokens nao funcionam cross-deploy).\n\nEndpoint: https://orcapi.martiellima.com/ (raiz) ou /graphql — ambos funcionam com POST.\n\nQUICK REFERENCE (queries marcadas com * precisam de token, ** precisam de admin):\n  Queries: health, me*, users**, clientes*, veiculos*, motoristas*, posicoesRecentes*, posicoesPorVeiculo*, syncStatus**, requestLog**, auditLog**, refreshTokens**, caixaPretaEventos*\n  Mutations: login, refresh, createUser**, updateUser**, deleteUser**, resetUserPassword**, revokeRefreshToken**",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Pre-request Script — auto-refresh do accessToken.",
          "// Roda antes de CADA request da collection (exceto onde sobrescrito).",
          "// Logica:",
          "//   1. Decodifica o payload do {{token}} e le o campo 'exp' (sem validar assinatura — UX apenas).",
          "//   2. Se ainda faltam > 30s para expirar, no-op.",
          "//   3. Se expirou (ou nao existe), chama 'mutation refresh' com {{refreshToken}}.",
          "//   4. Salva os novos tokens nas variaveis da collection e segue.",
          "//   5. Se o refresh falhar (token revogado/expirado), limpa as vars — faca Login novamente.",
          "",
          "const baseUrl = pm.collectionVariables.get('baseUrl');",
          "const token = pm.collectionVariables.get('token');",
          "const refreshToken = pm.collectionVariables.get('refreshToken');",
          "",
          "function decodeJwtExp(jwt) {",
          "  if (!jwt) return 0;",
          "  const part = jwt.split('.')[1];",
          "  if (!part) return 0;",
          "  try {",
          "    const pad = part + '='.repeat((4 - part.length % 4) % 4);",
          "    const payload = JSON.parse(atob(pad.replace(/-/g, '+').replace(/_/g, '/')));",
          "    return payload.exp || 0;",
          "  } catch (e) {",
          "    return 0;",
          "  }",
          "}",
          "",
          "async function callRefresh(rt) {",
          "  const res = await fetch(baseUrl, {",
          "    method: 'POST',",
          "    headers: {",
          "      'Content-Type': 'application/json',",
          "      'apollo-require-preflight': 'true'",
          "    },",
          "    body: JSON.stringify({",
          "      query: 'mutation R($rt: String!) { refresh(refreshToken: $rt) { accessToken refreshToken user { id email role } } }',",
          "      variables: { rt }",
          "    })",
          "  });",
          "  return res.json();",
          "}",
          "",
          "(async () => {",
          "  const exp = decodeJwtExp(token);",
          "  const now = Math.floor(Date.now() / 1000);",
          "  if (exp > now + 30) return;",
          "",
          "  if (!refreshToken) {",
          "    console.warn('[auto-refresh] sem refreshToken salvo — execute Login (admin) primeiro');",
          "    return;",
          "  }",
          "",
          "  try {",
          "    const json = await callRefresh(refreshToken);",
          "    if (json.data && json.data.refresh && json.data.refresh.accessToken) {",
          "      pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.refresh.accessToken);",
          "      pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refresh.refreshToken);",
          "      console.log('[auto-refresh] tokens renovados automaticamente');",
          "    } else {",
          "      pm.collectionVariables.unset('token');",
          "      pm.collectionVariables.unset('refreshToken');",
          "      console.error('[auto-refresh] refresh falhou — faca Login novamente', JSON.stringify(json));",
          "    }",
          "  } catch (e) {",
          "    console.error('[auto-refresh] erro de rede ao chamar refresh:', e.message);",
          "  }",
          "})();"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "https://orcapi.martiellima.com/",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "targetUserId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Setup",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.login && json.data.login.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.login.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.login.refreshToken);",
                  "  console.log('Tokens salvos — {{token}} (15min) e {{refreshToken}} (7d)');",
                  "  pm.test('login retornou refreshToken', () => pm.expect(json.data.login.refreshToken).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty);",
                  "} else {",
                  "  console.error('Login falhou:', JSON.stringify(json));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"mutation L($e: String!, $p: String!) { login(email: $e, password: $p) { accessToken refreshToken user { id email role } } }\",\"variables\":{\"e\":\"admin@local.dev\",\"p\":\"admin1234\"}}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (verifica token salvo)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"{ me { id email role active } }\"}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh (manual, raramente necessario)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"mutation R($rt: String!) { refresh(refreshToken: $rt) { accessToken refreshToken user { id email role } } }\",\"variables\":{\"rt\":\"{{refreshToken}}\"}}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Sanity checks",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health (publico)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"{ health }\"}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "auditLog sem token (esperado UNAUTHENTICATED)",
          "auth": {
            "type": "noauth"
          },
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"{ auditLog(limit: 1) { id } }\"}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Audit log queries (admin)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "auditLog (ultimos 10)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"{ auditLog(limit: 10) { id action targetTable targetId actorUserId ip userAgent createdAt diff } }\"}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "auditLog filtrado por action=user.password_reset",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"{ auditLog(action: \\\"user.password_reset\\\", limit: 20) { targetId actorUserId ip userAgent createdAt } }\"}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "auditLog filtrado por targetId={{targetUserId}}",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"query Q($t: String!) { auditLog(targetId: $t) { action ip userAgent diff createdAt } }\",\"variables\":{\"t\":\"{{targetUserId}}\"}}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Trigger audit entries (com user de teste)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar user de teste (grava user.create)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.createUser && json.data.createUser.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('targetUserId', json.data.createUser.id);",
                  "  console.log('targetUserId salvo:', json.data.createUser.id);",
                  "} else {",
                  "  console.error('createUser falhou:', JSON.stringify(json));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"mutation C($i: CreateUserInput!) { createUser(input: $i) { id email role active } }\",\"variables\":{\"i\":{\"email\":\"audit-postman-{{$timestamp}}@local.dev\",\"password\":\"PostmanAa1!\",\"role\":\"user\"}}}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset senha do user (grava user.password_reset)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"mutation R($id: ID!, $p: String!) { resetUserPassword(id: $id, newPassword: $p) { id } }\",\"variables\":{\"id\":\"{{targetUserId}}\",\"p\":\"ResetPostmanAa1!\"}}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update role do user (grava user.update)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"mutation U($id: ID!, $i: UpdateUserInput!) { updateUser(id: $id, input: $i) { id role active } }\",\"variables\":{\"id\":\"{{targetUserId}}\",\"i\":{\"active\":false}}}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verificar 3 entries do user de teste",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"query Q($t: String!) { auditLog(targetId: $t) { action ip userAgent diff createdAt } }\",\"variables\":{\"t\":\"{{targetUserId}}\"}}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Cleanup: deletar user de teste (grava user.delete)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "apollo-require-preflight", "value": "true" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"query\":\"mutation D($id: ID!) { deleteUser(id: $id) }\",\"variables\":{\"id\":\"{{targetUserId}}\"}}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
